race.comment: BADDA BOOM BABY (3) looks ready to peak now fourth-up after a sharp improvement last start when close-up in third over this track and trip. Well drawn, aided by the 3kg claim, and gets his chance to break through. MISHANI PERSUASION (5) has built nicely into his prep and was only a neck away at Dalby last time. Faces a stronger field but has the talent to measure up. OUT OF ACES (2) resumes and has a strong first-up record, placing in all three fresh runs to date. Trialled well and gets weight relief with the claim. Must be respected. UCELLE (16) improved sharply at Gatton when sticking on into the frame. Drawn to roll forward again and is one for the exotics.
